  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Ranger Trap</strong><br/><br/><p>Effect Lazurite radiation increases the victim's susceptibility to the attacks of undead creatures that are bolstered by the radiation. The target takes a -2 penalty to Armor Class against the attacks of undead creatures and on saving throws against effects created by undead. This effect lasts for 10 minutes per ranger level. A successful Will save negates this effect. If this is an extraordinary trap, the ranger must supply a sliver of lazurite.</p>",
